As for Sony breaking the contract I 100% agree with you.  FV was advertised as a RP preferred server and we were led to believe that it would remain that way by Sony.  After putting in countless hours and spending considerable amounts of money creating and building our characters, they have decided to change the ruleset which attracted us to the server in the first place.  <br>
<br>
In a sense this has devalued in my case the 2 characters I built here to such an extent that I am seriously considering terminating my two accounts.  My time and effort building these characters would be wasted in that case and i'm sure at least in my country I would be elligible for compensation for time and money lost.  <br>
<br>
You might laugh at that but its similiar to the post about the road going through someones house when they had previously been no indication that such a road was going through. The latter case obviously being more severe but there is a parallel.<br>
